                            <comment id="16750486" author="zsxwing" created="Wed, 23 Jan 2019 22:37:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;IIUC, this issue will cause a file deletion (delete the temp file) and a file rename (move the temp file to the target file) happen at the same time. Could you clarify why this will cause a task committed partial data? I think the file rename should either move the whole file to the target file, or just fail, right?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16750724" author="cloud_fan" created="Thu, 24 Jan 2019 04:54:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Issue resolved by pull request 23608&lt;br/&gt;
